    <p>Skye Freeman is a Product Engineer/Computer Programmer/Digital Craftsperson living in New York City. Born and raised in Brooklyn, he&rsquo;s the husband of Julia, Cat Dad of Maddux, Dog Dad of Pluto.</p>
