  <p>Skye&rsquo;s is in his second decade of tech work. He writes a lot of software, (some of which you may have used!). He&rsquo;s currently working on product at Aura Frames, and previously at Affirm, Venmo, Bloglovin&rsquo; and more. Sometimes he writes, mostly about what he learns while constructing software.</p>

  <p>He loves to run, swim and cycle. He thinks often about competing in Triathalons (maybe he&rsquo;ll eventually do one). He plays the guitar, reads sci-fi, plays independantly made video games, and learns about music production in his spare time.</p>
  
